{"tid":1361500,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"我呢個時間去旅行係咪錯","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T09:43:03.000Z","uid":24006,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"563a4cadee3dcacb1832402366d6e881c330434d","tid":1361500,"uid":24006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:24:59.000Z","msg":"A君問我出唔出元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話好耐之前屋企人定左要去轉外地<br />\n老豆成六十五歲都未搭過飛機，<br />\n一向腳又唔好，驚佢遲下行都行唔郁<br />\n呀哥平時做野好忙難得有假 我同佢宜家先叫有少少經濟能力<br />\n<br />\nA君知道即刻唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我記起元朗單野之後佢同我講話見到d人平日仲有講有笑覺得好嬲<br />\n<br />\n我究竟係咪唔啱?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都有一直發夢，A君幾次搵我我都有同佢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42231c09df3664df7da2530ccbd8a424cb2a16e6","tid":1361500,"uid":17325,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"照去，今次唔去下次唔知幾時齊人"},{"pid":"f4b9bf243582b467fa6947a86980f1a8f7b86219","tid":1361500,"uid":265696,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:38:09.000Z","msg":"去，除左義務，人重有權利<br />\n陪屋企人開開心心去玩，叉足電返黎"},{"pid":"0e252c3809868ba7e3122c98b5d0325a03210f8d","tid":1361500,"uid":70527,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"照去 長期抗爭 正常生活"},{"pid":"c2be033b050e71a4c0cd9d1b9dea65c023e74009","tid":1361500,"uid":119596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"去啦"},{"pid":"a0df11b570b38ec19065884126b6bf40b4581eb0","tid":1361500,"uid":82829,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:39:47.000Z","msg":"我去去就回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f24e481465beca3fd2e4067784fe1eedf44f3ab","tid":1361500,"uid":47020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"go"},{"pid":"bf31d4ae48b05742e97141a16c035792b8a42cf3","tid":1361500,"uid":279185,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"温題：其實你朋友情緒可能過份繃緊，你作為朋友應該輔導一下，通常這是到最後會諗埋一邊的前奏"},{"pid":"3107cca5a325288dcf44fb180053c21bad991add","tid":1361500,"uid":189158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:41:54.000Z","msg":"照去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25286372f90b6072b011e2255fe21a96177f4eea","tid":1361500,"uid":180745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:42:36.000Z","msg":"去啦 番黎再一齊抗爭<br />\n同父母玩得開心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b4445f5f754694615c2a9b0adc4e5340940a76","tid":1361500,"uid":8435,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"無問題<br />\n好好同屋企人一齊放鬆下<br />\n<br />\nA君無惡意嘅<br />\n只係佢拉得太緊<br />\n返嚟再一齊爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346fae7b52cc898a32f2e437cb83ef9a4acb0b38","tid":1361500,"uid":271309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:46:37.000Z","msg":"去唔到現場<br />\n當日用手機上網，幫手轉遞消息囉<br />\n咁樣都係幫"},{"pid":"99d1a26c6332e29f6dc5bd315fb5c68427f7ee3c","tid":1361500,"uid":268540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"有啲嘢而家唔做，將來實後悔"},{"pid":"146a0168bd5a2baf2c1b49a254866c269586c2ff","tid":1361500,"uid":162910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:49:58.000Z","msg":"去外國同memo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2fe69d1688fad4e73b3d689f4853da93eadfca","tid":1361500,"uid":61396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:17.000Z","msg":"緊張左成個月<br />\n休息完再戰 好合理<br />\n<br />\n這是一場長期戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n去旅行就唔好上網<br />\n放鬆下 <br />\n<br />\n返來再留意返<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有人 都需要合理休息<br />\n休息才可以長期作戰"},{"pid":"c5e0446711a9561b76c7bdc8cd28758ab07ac110","tid":1361500,"uid":210794,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"我過兩日都飛，<br />\n去兩個禮拜。<br />\n<br />\n成家人一齊去，<br />\n一早訂晒嘢，<br />\n無理由唔去⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我6.9到而家九成夢都有發，<br />\n屋企人都起碼六成。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話自己好大付出但起碼有努力過，<br />\n而家休息兩個禮拜都唔太過份啦。<br />\n<br />\n最緊要個心喺香港，<br />\n好好玩夠再歸隊！<br />\n<br />\n巴打祝你旅途愉快！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72cabe9cf596b99a9f7ed4de952b131daefa525","tid":1361500,"uid":72581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:55:26.000Z","msg":"A君自己都要放鬆下"},{"pid":"23215c4476cf6efa92309d9b7ef1674e38507e35","tid":1361500,"uid":271249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"去 放鬆下<br />\n得閒可以同外國朋友宣傳下"},{"pid":"7fafbc6bc7c005ec3c09da98af74055436263295","tid":1361500,"uid":284082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"去啦"},{"pid":"b3b932d652981103976f73ea7f62425e203f1150","tid":1361500,"uid":209026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:57:47.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 連登團結到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cde40fa89f3794d1362bda9a10a348ce5a69d9a","tid":1361500,"uid":273807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"屋企人同自己都好重要架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然努力左咁多次 咪放個假叉足電<br />\n<br />\n同A傾下 佢會明白既"},{"pid":"898a37cf5693c5430cb4b545591b35c74bbec673","tid":1361500,"uid":209026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"平時你地唔係咁 淨係會屌柒人"},{"pid":"11bc94d1f16e6a688c47ecf9fa431afea47472ec","tid":1361500,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"休息